---
title: About Us
description: Learn more about our team and mission
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="heading-1 text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">About Us</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We're passionate about creating beautiful, functional websites that make a difference.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-dark max-w-none">
        <p>
          Welcome to Middlemanplate, a modern starter template built with Ruby Middleman and Tailwind CSS. 
          Our goal is to provide developers with a solid foundation for building fast, beautiful static websites.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe that building websites should be enjoyable and efficient. That's why we've created 
          this template with all the essential features you need, so you can focus on what matters most: 
          creating great content and delivering value to your users.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Ruby Middleman</strong> - A powerful static site generator</li>
          <li><strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> - Utility-first CSS framework</li>
          <li><strong>Dark Mode</strong> - Built-in theme switching</li>
          <li><strong>Blog</strong> - Full-featured blog with tags and categories</li>
          <li><strong>SEO Optimized</strong> - Best practices for search engines</li>
          <li><strong>Responsive Design</strong> - Looks great on all devices</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Get Started</h2>
        <p>
          Ready to build your next project? Check out our 
          <a href="/blog/">blog</a> for tips and tutorials, or 
          <a href="/contact/">contact us</a> if you have any questions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Team Section -->
<section class="section bg-gray-50 dark:bg-dark-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="heading-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Meet Our Team</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">The people behind the project</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <% team_members = [
        { name: 'John Doe', role: 'Lead Developer', avatar: '/images/avatar.png' },
        { name: 'Jane Smith', role: 'Designer', avatar: '/images/avatar.png' },
        { name: 'Bob Wilson', role: 'Content Writer', avatar: '/images/avatar.png' }
      ] %>
      
      <% team_members.each do |member| %>
        <div class="card p-8 text-center card-hover">
          <img src="<%= member[:avatar] %>" 
               alt="<%= member[:name] %>" 
               class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">
            <%= member[:name] %>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"><%= member[:role] %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%= partial 'partials/call_to_action', locals: {
  title: 'Want to Work Together?',
  description: "We'd love to hear from you. Get in touch and let's create something amazing.",
  button_text: 'Contact Us',
  button_url: '/contact/'
} %>
